                "caption": "Figure 6:User study tasks and setup. Our subjects completed three tasks using a commercial virtual reality headset: “push the green button”, “open the jar”, and “turn the steering wheel”. Representative screenshots of all three tasks from the perspective seen by the user (top). A photo of our setup, in which the generated video’s hands reflect the user’s in real-time (bottom).",
                "position": 985
            },
